I know people aren't looking for nuance in the comments on nhentai, but I see a lot of "she's a slut" and "you're just mad she's not a virgin" and thought I might as well wax philosophically on porn for a bit.

Yeah, the art is great, virginity has never been make or break for me, and I could probably crank one out, but this really didn't do it for me. A girl who comes onto you because she knew you a decade ago and asks you to impregnate her the same day (pg 39) is setting off too many alarm bells for me to get aroused.

And yeah, "it's just fantasy, it doesn't need to be realistic" is a valid counterpoint to address that concern. People are free to fantasize about whatever they want. I just prefer to fantasize about people who have sex me for better reasons than "got a big dick" or "we knew each other a really long time ago". Anyone reading this comment should have more to offer than that, the bar is so low it's on the floor.

Anyway, 11/10 - she has tanlines.
